INFORMATION : Punta Helbronner lifts ITALY
From March 24th to April 6th included, the Punta Helbronner lifts that allow you to descend to the Torino Refuge will be closed due to exceptional maintenance work.
Access to the glacier will be possible ONLY via the climbers' exit at level 0 of the Punta Helbronner site.
